---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Male Transformation Over 40">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6">Welcome to Male Transformation Over 40, your trusted resource for health, fitness, and wellness information specifically tailored for men over 40.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">Our mission is to empower men over 40 with the knowledge, tools, and support they need to achieve their optimal health and fitness goals. We understand the unique challenges that come with maintaining fitness and wellness as we age, and we're here to help you navigate this journey successfully.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Expert guidance on fitness and nutrition</li>
        <li>Age-appropriate workout programs</li>
        <li>Nutritional advice for optimal health</li>
        <li>Community support and motivation</li>
        <li>Latest research and health insights</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you. Contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@maletransformationover40.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">info@maletransformationover40.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
